snippet.title: American Pool basic shots physics on slow motion - ShootersPool Billiards Simulation
snippet.description:
This is a video demonstration of the ShootersPool Billiards Simulation physics engine showing some american pool basic shots on slow motion.

Some of the shots that you can watch on the video are Back Spin, Top Spin, Drag Shot, Stun Shots, Side Spin, Top Right Spin, Masse Shot and Cue Ball Bouncing with the Cushions.

For recording this video, we have set a white cue ball with red dots in order to show you the cue ball behavior on the different american pool shots.

Hope you enjoy it pool players 🙂.
